data.description: Welcome home to this well maintained 2 bedroom, 1 full bathroom and 1/2 bath single family home that is quite comfortable and cozy.  From the moment you step inside, you'll see great hardwood floors that lead you through the spacious and airy living areas. The  kitchen has space for an eat-in dining area.  The bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of closet space.  Enjoy the tranquility of your neighborhood from the charming front porch or tuck away in an oversized two-car garage for ultimate privacy. Located in a highly desirable area, this home offers easy access to everything you need. Whether you're looking to dine out, shop, or explore the great outdoors, you are close to a lot of great attractions.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule your viewing today!
